SNB’s Annual Dividend May Drop to 1 Billion Francs, NZZ Says

-- B y   G i l e s   B r o o m
-- 
2011-03-31T07:02:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-31/snb-s-annual-dividend-may-drop-to-1-billion-francs-nzz-says.html
The Swiss central bank’s annual
dividend paid to the federal and regional governments may
decline to 1 billion francs, Neue Zuercher Zeitung said, citing
Fritz Zurbruegg, head of the Federal Finance Department, and
Pankraz Freitag, a lawmaker.  The  Swiss National Bank  paid out 2.5 billion francs last
year, the paper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Giles Broom in Zurich at 
 gbroom@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Rummer at   arummer@bloomberg.net . 